  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-01-12",
    "date": "2021-02-18T19:35:33Z",
    "text": "Require USCP to Utilize Body-Worn Cameras Act\n\nThis bill requires each uniformed officer of the U.S. Capitol Police whose job duties include interacting with the general public to use a body-worn camera and ensure it is activated while on duty. This requirement does not apply to an officer serving on a personal protection detail."
